"result of a garden ``Propagation``.  This information is optional.  A "
"successful ``Propagation`` trial can only result in one accession (0..1),"
" while a ``Contact`` may provide multiple ``Accessions`` (0..n)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../goal.rst:69
msgid ""
